  "travelConnectors": [
    "The route ahead is open but the heat builds steadily.",
    "Fresh tracks cross the path. Something large passed recently.",
    "A wrecked skiff sits half-buried in the sand. The cargo is gone.",
    "The horizon shimmers. Could be a mirage. Could be smoke.",
    "An old way marker stands here, pointing three directions.",
    "The wind picks up. Dust on the eastern edge.",
    "Bones of a large animal. Picked clean. Recent.",
    "A dry riverbed cuts across the path. Crossable but slow.",
    "Distant fire at night. Origin unclear.",
    "The road narrows to a single track through loose sand.",
    "Evidence of a camp, abandoned in a hurry.",
    "A stretch of ancient paved road surfaces briefly, then vanishes.",
    "Vultures circling something ahead and to the north.",
    "The temperature drops sharply. The terrain is shifting.",
    "A lone figure on the ridge. Gone by the time you look again.",
    "Salt crust underfoot. The ground here is hollow.",
    "Storm debris scattered across the route. Recent passage was rough.",
    "A Camelon trail marker. Someone knows this path.",
    "Silence. No insects, no wind. Uncomfortable quiet.",
    "The sand here has an unusual color. Red-orange, almost rust."
